{
  "stem": "2460.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were scared to death because we couldn't understand from the beginning those animals who were beating them, literally breaking their bones-- not to hit them over the head so they should die right away.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Just breaking them pieces.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And you see human flesh and blood and human waste all over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was the worst, worst picture that I-- [COUGHS] I saw people die.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I saw people taken almost-- they still breathing-- and taken away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Of course, we knew they're taking away to bury them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But here they were beating them to death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I just-- it was something very, very frightening, a picture that will never ever will forget.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was something unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was an unwritten law, later I found out, that kapos from one camp shouldn't take over their jobs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was a-- it was a-- they were beat-- they knew exactly who were the kapos because they have list of people, and the Germans also gave them the list of the kapos.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they knew exactly who to grab and who to beat to death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of them survived, just a miracle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of them survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His Polish friends helped him, and they bandaged him with paper bandages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he hanged himself next day because he wouldn't be able to leave, anyway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was all broken pieces.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he hanged himself and we walked out in the morning and I saw him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He hung himself on a rope-- not on a rope, on a belt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe somebody assisted him, because wouldn't be able to do by himself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he died, also.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think he wanted to die because, without medicine and without painkillers, the man was bleeding and broken.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wasn't able even to move his hands or his legs.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
